name: WithinMe
description:
WithinMe is a game that tells about an unknown Traveler that were cursed by an Evil Witch that splits his souls into two and the Traveler need to collect 5 magic artefact in the forest to become whole again.

Made With : Unity Engine

CONTROLS :

D - MOVE FORWARD

A - MOVE BACKWARD

SPACE - JUMP
